-----------------			
criteria------>sql---execute---slower						
-------------------------------------------		
HQL : hibernte query lanaguage
	-object oriented queries
	- * not allow
	-performance wise faster than criteria
	- Query query=session.createQuery(hql);
		
-----------	
SQL : select * from employee; (table name)
HQL : from Employee; (Class name)

SQL :  select name from employee where username="admin" and password="admin";
HQL :  select name from Employee where userName=:un and password="admin";	

---------------------------------------------
SQL : SQLQuery squery=session.createSQLQuery(sql);		
